    <item>
      <title>雪佛龙将总部从加利福尼亚州迁至德克萨斯州</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-02/chevron-is-moving-headquarters-from-california-to-texas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雪佛龙表示将把总部从加州迁至德克萨斯。这家能源巨头现在将落户休斯顿。首席执行官迈克·沃思表示，休斯顿是“世界能源之都”，也是该行业的中心。他接受了彭博社的 Alix Steel 的采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-02/chevron-is-moving-headquarters-from-california-to-texas</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 13:36:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国人民银行将加大对经济的支持力度，重点转向消费</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/pboc-to-step-up-support-for-economy-shifts-focus-to-consumption</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行表示，该国银行必须采取更多措施促进实体经济，这是其重振国内低迷消费的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/pboc-to-step-up-support-for-economy-shifts-focus-to-consumption</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 13:27:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国拒绝越南取消“非市场经济”标签的请求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/us-rejects-vietnam-s-request-to-lift-non-market-economy-tag</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府拒绝了越南正式将其列为“市场经济”的请求，这对越南扩大对最重要市场出口的努力造成了挫折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/us-rejects-vietnam-s-request-to-lift-non-market-economy-tag</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 13:24:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德的罗森伯格表示市场仍希望 9 月降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-02/blackrock-s-rosenberg-says-markets-still-want-a-september-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德投资组合经理杰弗里·罗森伯格表示，7 月份的就业报告令人失望，美联储可能不愿在 9 月份降息 50 个基点。但他表示，市场希望看到降息。他正在接受“彭博监测”的采访。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-02/blackrock-s-rosenberg-says-markets-still-want-a-september-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 13:15:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Iberdrola 将斥资 21 亿英镑收购英国电网股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/iberdrola-to-buy-stake-in-uk-power-network-for-2-1-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊比德罗拉公司 (Iberdrola SA) 已同意从由关西电力株式会社、Equitix Ltd 和 CNIC Funds LLC 牵头的财团手中收购英国曼彻斯特电网运营商 Electricity North-West 88% 的股份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/iberdrola-to-buy-stake-in-uk-power-network-for-2-1-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 13:13:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>彼得森称市场对就业报告反应过度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-02/markets-are-overreacting-to-jobs-report-peterson-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界大型企业联合会首席经济学家达娜·彼得森表示，市场对 7 月份就业报告反应过度，而且数据仍然强劲。她正在接受“彭博监测”采访。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-02/markets-are-overreacting-to-jobs-report-peterson-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 13:08:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>雪佛龙因规则警告退出加州，转投德州</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/chevron-misses-earnings-estimates-adding-to-hess-delay-pressure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雪佛龙公司 (Chevron Corp.) 正在将总部从加利福尼亚迁至休斯顿，此前该公司曾多次警告称，加州的监管制度使美国成为难以开展业务的地方。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/chevron-misses-earnings-estimates-adding-to-hess-delay-pressure</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 10:16:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于美国数据疲软，科技股暴跌，欧洲股市抛售加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/european-stocks-extend-drop-amid-global-selloff-before-us-jobs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国就业报告弱于预期，引发人们对经济增长的担忧，并加剧了科技股的暴跌，欧洲股市延续跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/european-stocks-extend-drop-amid-global-selloff-before-us-jobs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 07:16:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>梅洛尼再次考虑对意大利银行征税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/italy-may-consider-a-levy-on-profits-of-banks-energy-firms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼正在寻找从银行业筹集更多资金的方法，以期在意大利公共财政紧缩的情况下赢得选民的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/italy-may-consider-a-levy-on-profits-of-banks-energy-firms</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 07:03:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业加剧“增长恐慌” 股市抛售加剧：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[疲软的就业报告引发人们对美联储降息步伐过慢的担忧，导致股市抛售加剧，债券收益率暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 22:41:21 GMT</pubDate>
